    sources: "<a href='https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Reference/Values/random' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>MDN — random() CSS function (grammar, sharing keys, 'not Baseline', @supports fallback + a11y warning)</a> · <a href='https://css-tricks.com/almanac/functions/r/random/' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>CSS-Tricks — random() almanac entry</a> · <a href='https://www.sitepoint.com/css-mathrandom-in-production-native-randomness-without-javascript/' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>SitePoint — Native randomness in CSS without JavaScript (Safari 26.2, fallbacks)</a> · <a href='https://blog.cloudflare.com/introducing-precursor/' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>Cloudflare Blog — Introducing Precursor: continuous client-side agent detection (~57% bots)</a> · <a href='https://siliconangle.com/2026/07/13/cloudflare-launches-precursor-catch-bots-watching-entire-sessions/' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>SiliconANGLE — Cloudflare Precursor watches entire sessions</a> · <a href='https://www.cloudflare.com/application-services/products/turnstile/' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>Cloudflare — Turnstile (free CAPTCHA replacement, any plan)</a> · <a href='https://www.seroundtable.com/chatgpt-ads-attributed-sales-value-and-sales-roas-41674.html' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>Search Engine Roundtable — ChatGPT Ads Manager adds Attributed Sales Value &amp; Sales ROAS + product reporting</a> · <a href='https://receptivemedia.co.uk/openai-ads-manager-first-look/' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>Receptive Media — Inside the OpenAI/ChatGPT Ads Manager (campaign wizard, 4-step conversion pipeline, SFTP feed)</a> · <a href='https://help.openai.com/en/articles/20001268-create-campaigns-from-product-feeds' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>OpenAI Help — Create campaigns from product feeds</a> · <a href='https://www.socialmediatoday.com/news/instagram-reels-adds-more-ai-translations/825258/' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>Social Media Today — Instagram Reels adds more AI translations</a> · <a href='https://creators.instagram.com/blog/meta-ai-translations' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>Instagram for Creators — Meta AI translations for Reels (voice-mimicking dub + lip-sync)</a> · <a href='https://wersm.com/meta-makes-reels-easier-to-watch-across-languages/' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>WERSM — Meta expands AI translation for Reels</a> · <a href='https://www.searchenginejournal.com/chatgpt-access-tied-to-9-drop-in-traditional-search/582167/' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>Search Engine Journal — ChatGPT access tied to a 9% drop in traditional search (Bocconi study)</a> · <a href='https://ppc.land/wider-chatgpt-search-access-cuts-traditional-search-9-4-study-finds/' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>PPC Land — Wider ChatGPT access cuts traditional search 9.4% (Comscore, 45k+ households; 5.2% vs 31.1% referrals)</a> · <a href='https://www.hubspot.com/aeo-grader' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>HubSpot — Free AEO Grader (ChatGPT/Gemini/Perplexity snapshot)</a> · <a href='https://www.semrush.com/free-tools/ai-search-visibility-checker/' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>Semrush — Free AI Search Visibility Checker</a> · <a href='https://www.litmus.com/blog/your-holiday-emails-start-now-a-summer-deliverability-prep-guide' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>Litmus — Your Holiday Emails Start Now: A Summer Deliverability Prep Guide (Jul 9 2026)</a> · <a href='https://postmaster.google.com/' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>Google Postmaster Tools</a> · <a href='https://sendersupport.olc.protection.outlook.com/snds/' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>Microsoft SNDS (Outlook/Hotmail sender IP reputation + JMRP)</a> · <a href='https://www.cnbc.com/2026/07/15/asml-2q-earnings-ai-chips-orders.html' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>CNBC — ASML raises 2026 forecast a 2nd time on strong AI chip demand (Q2 €9.3B)</a> · <a href='https://www.cnbc.com/2026/07/15/sk-hynix-asia-tech-stocks-rally-.html' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>CNBC — SK Hynix jumps ~8% as Asia tech stocks rally</a> · <a href='https://www.washingtonpost.com/technology/2026/07/14/new-york-becomes-first-state-impose-data-center-moratorium/' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>Washington Post — New York becomes first state to impose a data-center moratorium</a> · <a href='https://www.cnbc.com/2026/07/10/apple-openai-lawsuit-trade-secrets.html' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>CNBC — Apple sues OpenAI alleging trade-secret theft 'at every level'</a> · <a href='https://www.theverge.com/tech/965486/meta-lawsuit-former-employees-ai-layoffs' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>The Verge — Meta sued over allegedly biased-AI layoffs</a> · <a href='https://www.theverge.com/tech/964714/siri-ai-public-beta-preview-ios-27-hands-on' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>The Verge — Apple's new Siri AI in the iOS 27 public beta</a> · <a href='https://openrouter.ai/rankings' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>OpenRouter — LLM Rankings by token volume (GLM-5.2 ~#4 overall)</a> · <a href='https://openrouter.ai/collections/programming' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>OpenRouter — Best models for coding (Hy3 / MiMo-V2.5 / DeepSeek V4 Flash lead by token volume)</a>"
