    sources: "<a href='https://developer.chrome.com/blog/a-customizable-select' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>Chrome for Developers — The &lt;select&gt; element can now be customized with CSS</a> · <a href='https://webkit.org/blog/18117/the-golden-rule-of-customizable-select/' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>WebKit — The golden rule of Customizable Select (coming to Safari 27)</a> · <a href='https://web-platform-dx.github.io/web-features-explorer/features/field-sizing/' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>web-features explorer — field-sizing (Baseline Newly Available 2026-06-16)</a> · <a href='https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/field-sizing' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>MDN — field-sizing (values + applicable elements)</a> · <a href='https://vercel.com/blog/dockerfile-on-vercel' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>Vercel Blog — Run any Dockerfile on Vercel</a> · <a href='https://vercel.com/changelog/ai-gateway-routing-rules' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>Vercel — Routing rules now available on AI Gateway</a> · <a href='https://vercel.com/changelog/model-fallbacks-now-available-in-vercel-ai-gateway' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>Vercel — Model fallbacks in AI Gateway (~3.5% complete via fallback)</a> · <a href='https://www.anthropic.com/news/claude-sonnet-5' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>Anthropic — Introducing Claude Sonnet 5</a> · <a href='https://www.marktechpost.com/2026/06/30/anthropic-claude-sonnet-5-vs-sonnet-4-6-vs-opus-4-8-agentic-coding-benchmarks-api-pricing-and-cost-performance-tradeoffs-compared/' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>MarkTechPost — Sonnet 5 vs Sonnet 4.6 vs Opus 4.8 (benchmarks + pricing)</a> · <a href='https://www.recraft.ai/blog/new-tools-for-brand-style-consistency-and-control' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>Recraft Blog — New tools for brand style consistency and control</a> · <a href='https://higgsfield.ai/ai-product-photography' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>Higgsfield — AI Product Photography (photo-to-catalog pipeline)</a> · <a href='https://higgsfield.ai/soul' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>Higgsfield — Soul (fashion-grade photo model + Soul ID)</a> · <a href='https://www.litmus.com/blog/what-is-microsoft-snds-why-your-deliverability-strategy-depends-on-it' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>Litmus — What Is Microsoft SNDS (and the Jun 2026 changes)</a> · <a href='https://sendersupport.olc.protection.outlook.com/snds/index' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>Microsoft — Smart Network Data Services (SNDS)</a> · <a href='https://searchengineland.com/google-adds-channel-diagnostics-to-performance-max-481445' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>Search Engine Land — Google adds Channel Diagnostics to Performance Max</a> · <a href='https://www.socialmediatoday.com/news/reddit-rolls-out-split-testing-to-all-advertisers/824298/' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>Social Media Today — Reddit rolls out split testing to all advertisers</a> · <a href='https://techcrunch.com/2026/06/27/instagram-is-testing-more-ways-for-users-to-customize-your-algorithm/' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>TechCrunch — Instagram is testing more ways to customize Your Algorithm</a> · <a href='https://www.socialmediatoday.com/news/x-launches-livestream-studio-to-simplify-live-broadcasts/824300/' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>Social Media Today — X launches livestream studio</a> · <a href='https://baymard.com/lists/cart-abandonment-rate' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>Baymard Institute — Cart Abandonment Rate research</a> · <a href='https://www.shopify.com/blog/average-order-value' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>Shopify — Average Order Value guide</a> · <a href='https://www.cnbc.com/2026/07/02/alphabet-google-android-eu-antitrust-fine-4-1-billion-euro-appeal.html' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>CNBC — Google loses fight over record €4.1B EU antitrust fine</a> · <a href='https://www.cnbc.com/2026/07/02/openai-proposes-us-government-own-5percent-stake-to-address-political-blowback.html' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>CNBC — OpenAI proposes 5% stake to the US government</a> · <a href='https://ng.investing.com/news/stock-market-news/anthropic-targets-loopholes-used-by-chinese-firms-to-access-claude-ft-reports-2585575' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>Investing.com — Anthropic targets loopholes used by Chinese firms to access Claude (FT)</a> · <a href='https://techcrunch.com/2026/07/02/mark-zuckerberg-tells-staff-that-ai-agents-havent-progressed-as-quickly-as-hed-hoped/' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>TechCrunch — Zuckerberg: AI agents haven't progressed as quickly as hoped</a> · <a href='https://www.cnbc.com/2026/06/29/spacex-debt-diversification-equity-bond-investors-analysts.html' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>CNBC — SpaceX's $25B bond sale: huge demand, and a potential headache</a> · <a href='https://www.cnbc.com/2026/07/02/samsung-sk-hynix-shares-slide-kospi-tech-selloff-nasdaq.html' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>CNBC — Samsung, SK Hynix tumble as chip rout spreads</a>"
